%N A397611 Decimal expansion of the midradius of a canonical (dual-uniform) hexagonal trapezohedron with unit short edge length.
%C A397611 The hexagonal trapezohedron is the dual polyhedron of the hexagonal antiprism.
%H A397611 Paolo Xausa, <a href="/A397611/b397611.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..10000</a>
%H A397611 David I. McCooey, <a href="https://dmccooey.com/polyhedra/HexagonalTrapezohedron.html">Hexagonal Trapezohedron</a>.
