%H A397611 <a href="/index/Al#algebraic_04">Index entries for algebraic numbers, degree 4</a>.
%F A397611 Equals sqrt(5 + 3*sqrt(3))/2 = sqrt(5 + A010482)/2.
%F A397611 Equals the largest real root of 8*x^4 - 20*x^2 - 1.
%e A397611 1.5965707330640437272569881052455809967649803272116...
%t A397611 First[RealDigits[Sqrt[5 + Sqrt[27]]/2, 10, 100]]
